I '''Ravi Shankar''' ({{lang-bn|রবি শংকর}}; mibait '''Robindro Shaunkor Chowdhury''', 7 Abril 1920{{spaced ndash}}11 Diciembre 2012<ref name="hindu">{{cite news| url=http://www.thehindu.com/arts/music/sitar-maestro-ravi-shankar-passes-away/article4190878.ece| title=Pandit Ravi Shankar passes away| work=[[The Hindu]]| date=12 December 2012| accessdate=12 December 2012| last=Ganapathy |first=Lata}}</ref>), a maralas dang awsan king kayang titulung [[Pandit]], metung yang [[India]]nung musikeru ampong kompositor a titigtig king [[sitar]], metung a instrumentung kakalbitan kwerdas. Sasabyan dang ya ing pikabalwab diling musikerong Indianu king salukuyan.<ref name="Neuhoff">Neuhoff 2006, pp. 672–673</ref>

Mibait ya i Shankar king [[Varanasi]], at anyang kayang kayanakan, miglakbe ya king Europa ampong India kayabe ya ing grupung talaterak ning kapatad nang lalaking i [[Uday Shankar]]. Tinuknang yang teterak anyang 1938 ba yang manigaral king pamanigtig ''sitar'', at tinigtig ya antimong kasaup ning musikerong pang-korting i [[Allauddin Khan]]. Kayari ning kayang pamagaral anyang 1944, megobra ya i Shankar antimong kompositor, at lelangan na ing musika para king  ''[[The Apu Trilogy|Apu Trilogy]]'' nang [[Satyajit Ray]], at ya ing direktor king musika ning [[All India Radio]], New Delhi, manibat 1949 anggang 1956.

Anyang 1956, miglakbe ya king Europa ampo reng America a titigtig king [[musikang klasikung Indianu]] (''Indian classical music'') at pepasikat ne iti karin anyang dekadang 1960 kapamilatan ning pamanuru, pamanigtig, ampo king kayang pamiugnayan king biolinistang i [[Yehudi Menuhin]] ampo ing musikerung [[musikang rock|rock]] i [[George Harrison]] ning [[The Beatles]]. Miugne ya i Shankar king musika ning Albugan kapamilatan ning pamanyulat concerti para king for ''sitar'' ampo king orkesta, at mig-tour ya king yatu anyang dekadang 1970 ampong 1980. Manibat 1986 anggang 1992, migsilbi ya antimong menominang kayanib ning matas nang kapulungan ning [[Parlamentu ning India]]. Mibye ya kang Shankar ing pekamatas nang galal a sibilyan ning India, ing [[Bharat Ratna]], anyang 1999, at tinanggapp yang atlung [[Grammy Award]]. Sindu na ing pamanigtig king publiku kaybat ning banwang 2000, maralas kayabe ya ing kayang mas anak a anak a babai, i  [[Anoushka Shankar|Anoushka]].

